<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <h2 style="color: #007bff;">New Message Received</h2>

    <p>Hello {{ interpreterName }},</p>

    <p>You have received a new message from a client regarding request:</p>

    <blockquote style="padding: 10px; background: #f6f6f6; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
      {{ requestTitle }}
    </blockquote>

    <p>Message:</p>
    <blockquote style="font-style: italic; padding-left: 10px; border-left: 3px solid #888;">
      "{{ content }}"
    </blockquote>

    <p>You can respond by logging into your interpreter dashboard.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Best regards,<br>
      <strong>Interpreter Platform Team</strong>
    </p>

